quran[70]{c,v,t}:
  26,111,Jiseuot sigra peue tajak peugah Ek kamoe pateh nyan narit gata Nyang ikot gata cit awak reundah Rakan gata dum cit hina dina
  26,112,Geukheun boh hana nyang jeuet lon peugah Hana lon teupeue dum buet ureueng nyan
  26,113,Keunira gopnyan sideh bak Allah Meunyo tateupeue Po lon nyang kira
  26,114,Ureueng nyan teuma han jeuet lon keubah Han roe lon use ureueng meuiman
  26,115,Peuingat mantong dilon lon peugah Lon nyoe peuingat sagai nyang nyata
  26,116,Jikheun treuk boh ka bek le tapeugah Meunyo han taiem hai Noh digata Meurajam gata jinoe le bagah
  26,117,Kheun Noh Tuhanku pakri kaom lon Han jipateh lon jikheun beurakah
  26,118,Neubuka jalan keu lon nibak jih Neubri lon bak jih jinoe le beu glah Ngon dum rakan lon ureueng meuiman
  26,119,Teuma Noh lheueh nyan Kamoe peuleupah Ngon rakan gopnyan geu-ek lam kapai Nyang peunoh beukai dum ngon blah bicah
  26,120,Awak nyang tinggai laen nibak nyan Kamoe peukaram lam laot luah
  26,121,Atra nyan bandum sit jeuet keu tanda Allah Taʻala Kuasa leupah Teuma le that jih han jimeuiman Dijih bandum nyan hana phaedah
  26,122,Keubit Po gata Maha Peurkasa Lom pih Po gata Maha Peumurah
  26,123,Jikheun lom le ‘Ad sulet dum Rasul Han jitem kaboi peue nyang Hud peugah
  26,124,Chedara jih Hud geukheun bak jih nyan Pakon gata han takwa keu Allah
  26,125,Lon nyoe bit Rasul jeuet tapeucaya
  26,126,Teuma takwa gata keu Allah Tataʻat keu lon nyang Rasul gata
  26,127,Hana bak gata lon lakee upah Bak Po dum alam upah lon ka na
  26,128,Pakon tabina geudong dum meugah Pat-pat tanoh cot tapeudong geudong Teumpat tameuʻen meumewah-mewah
  26,129,Tapeugot kota dum ban saboh nyan Takira dum nyan han le takeubah f Tapike keukaiteuh sinan sabe Sang han le mateteuh meunan ulah
  26,130,‘Oh tapeuleumah droeteuh kuasa Angkara murka lalem sileupah Leupah that keujam buetteuh di gata
  26,131,Teuma takwa jinoe keu Allah Tataʻat keu lon nyang Rasul gata
  26,132,Nikmat keu gata Neubri le leupah d Tateupeue nikmat le that keu gata Nyankeuh tatakwa mantong keu Allah
  26,133,Padum na Neubri binatang teurnak Neubri ngon aneukteuh le sileupah
  26,134,Padum na keubon ngon ie mon mata
  26,135,Teuma keu gata lon takot salah Lon takot azeueb Neubri keu gata Bak uroe gata teurimong balah Uroe kiamat haro hara that
  26,136,Jiseuot leugat peue roe tapeugah Tabri nasehat keunoe keu kamoe À Saban bak kamoe ngon han tapeugah Saban ngon hana tabri nasehat
  26,137,Buet nyoe cit adat masa nyang sudah Ureueng dileekon pih buetgeuh meunoe
  26,138,Teuma keu kamoe han roe geubalah Hana geuazeueb bandum na kamoe
  26,139,Meu gata sidroe nyang sulet leupah Keu Rasul Kamoe jikheun doseuta Meupeubinasa treuk jih dum bagah Atra nyan bandum pih jeuet keu tanda Allah Taʻala Kuasa leupah Teuma le that jih han jimeuiman Keu jih bandum nyan hana phaedah
  26,140,Keubit Po gata Maha Peurkasa Lom pih Po gata Maha Peumurah
  26,141,Tsamud pih jikheun sulet dum Rasul Han jitem kaboi peue Shaleh peugah
  26,142,Geukheun le Shaleh chedara jih nyan Pakon gata han takwa keu Allah
  26,143,Lon nyoe bit Rasul jeuet tapeucaya
  26,144,Teuma takwa gata keu Allah Tataʻat keu lon nyang Rasul gata
  26,145,Hana bak gata lon lakee upah Upah lon ka na bak Po dum alam
  26,146,Ek gata aman sinoe geukeubah Peue han meuminah gata dum sinoe Dalam nanggroe nyoe amanteuh leupah
  26,147,Lam keubon-keubon ngon ie mon mata
  26,148,Lom nyang tapula tanaman indah Mayam keureuma meuayon-ayon Ngon leumiek leumbon galakteuh leupah
  26,149,Tapeugot rumoh tapheuet dum gunong Tapeubuet ceumong ngon reuoh reuah Hekteuh ngon payah hana takira
  26,150,Teuma takwa jinoe keu Allah Tataʻat keu lon nyang Rasul gata
  26,151,Bek le digata tapeubuet salah Awak nyang lalem bek le taikot
  26,152,Jipeubuet karot di bumoe Allah Jipeubuet fased kon jipeubuet got
  26,153,Jiseuot leugat peue roe tapeugah Ka jipeusihe gata dih lagoe
  26,154,Gata ngon kamoe saban that leupah Gata ngon kamoe sit manusia Boh teh keu tanda peuleumah bagah Meu nyo bit gata ureueng nyang beuna
  26,155,Nyoe saboh unta Shaleh kheun bagah Dijih na watee jijeb ie keudroe Digata keudroe tajeb puleh grah Uroe ie gata bagi bandua
  26,156,Teuma bek gata tapeubuet salah Bek taelanya teuma unta nyan Keu gata Tuhan teuma Neubalah Uroe kiamat uroe that raya Neuʻazeueb gata teuma le Allah
  26,157,Jitop ngon leumbeng teuma unta nyan Dijih ‘oh lheueh nyan meunyeusai teulah
  26,158,Teuma geuʻazeueb treuk dum awak nyan Sabab buet jih nyan raya that salah Bandum atra nyan pih jeuet keu tanda Allah Taʻala Kuasa leupah Teuma le that jih han jimeuiman Kon na atra nyan jitueng phaedah
  26,159,Keubit Po gata Maha Peurkasa Lom pih Po gata Maha Peumurah
  26,160,Kaom Luth jikheun sulet cit Rasul Han jitem kaboi peue nyang geupeugah
  26,161,Chedara jih Luth geukheun bak jih nyan Pakon gata han takwa keu Allah
  26,162,Lon nyoe bit Rasul jeuet tapeucaya
  26,163,Teuma takwa gata keu Allah Tataʻat keu lon nyang Rasul gata
  26,164,Hana bak gata lon lakee upah Bak Po dum alam upah lon ka na
  26,165,Pakon dum gata tapeubuet salah Tamita agam dum manusia Nyang aneuk dara bandum takeubah
  26,166,Takeubah inong peurumoh gata Nyang ka keu gata Neubri le Allah Jeuet gata teuma kaom elanya
  26,167,Jiseuot sigra peue roe tapeugah Hai Luth digata meu han tapiyoh Keudeh meuparoh dalam blang luah Meunyo han taiem meuuse gata
  26,168,Geukheun treuk sigra dilon ka sudah Buet gata dum nyan dilon that beunci
  26,169,Tuhanku Neubri lon nyoe beu leupah Lon ngon ahli lon bek roh bak buet jih Keubit dum buet jih raya that salah
  26,170,Kamoe peuleupah treuk teuma gopnyan Ngon ahli gopnyan laju Meupeuglah
  26,171,Meulengkan inong peurumoh gopnyan Roh lam kawan nyan awak nyang salah
  26,172,Nyang laen bandum Meupeubinasa
  26,173,Ujeuen kreueh raya keu jih Meuruah Ngon ujeuen batee Kamoe geulawa Sabab keu jih ka geuba peurintah Sijeuheut ujeuen keu jih jirasa Jikheun dusta keu Rasul Allah
  26,174,Atra nyan bandum pih jeuet keu tanda Allah Taʻala Kuasa leupah Teuma le that jih han jimeuiman Hana atra nyan jitueng phaedah
  26,175,Keubit Po gata Maha Peurkasa Lom pih Po gata Maha Peumurah
  26,176,Kaom Aikah pih peusulet Rasul Han jitem kaboi peue nyang geupeugah
  26,177,Geukheun le Syuʻib ubak awak nyan Pakon gata han takwa keu Allah
  26,178,Lon nyoe bit Rasul jeuet tapeucaya
  26,179,Teuma takwa gata keu Allah Tataʻat keu lon nyang Rasul gata
  26,180,Hana bak gata lon lakee upah Upah lon ka na bak Po dum alam